SOURCE LOCATION

The complete source files for this hardware design are available at:
https://github.com/Hessevalentino/Pyramid-PCB-Inspection-Fixture

Source files include:
  - pyramid.ipt (Autodesk Inventor Part - editable source)
  - pyramid.idw (Autodesk Inventor Drawing - technical documentation)
  - pyramid.stl (STL for 3D printing - ESD version)
  - pyramid-NOesd.stl (STL for 3D printing - non-ESD version)
  - pyramid.pdf (Technical drawing and specifications)

================================================================================

INDUSTRY COMPLIANCE

This design was developed for automotive industry applications and is intended
for use with PCB inspection in Class 3 environments according to IPC-A-610.

ESD Compliance: IEC 61340-5-1
Industry Sector: Automotive
Application: PCB microscopic inspection fixture

